From e0dfb696cea4d6467f99f4d78f9d19f451f8efdf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 16:49:29 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 13/42] Per-tab pane routing and auto-exit

The pane_id fled its process cage,
Now each tab stamps its own front page.
Resize finds its mark by name,
And when the last tab ends the game,
The server exits, stage by stage.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
